ams The alleged violations occurred in 1985 and 1986 at furniture, department, discount, appliance, do-it-yourself, and lawn and garden stores nationwide where <ORGANIZATION> GE </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Capital </ORGANIZATION> offered credit for consumer purchases.
