 ELSEWHERE IN TELEVISION _ As of tonight, <ORGANIZATION> ABC </ORGANIZATION>'s new `` <PERSON> Doogie </PERSON> <PERSON> Howser </PERSON>, M.D.,'' and `` Anything But Love'' are trading time slots in the lineup, with `` Doogie'' starting tonight at 9 p.m. EDT, followed by the other sitcom. <ORGANIZATION> ABC </ORGANIZATION> says `` Anything'' has shown a greater appeal to adults and thus is a better lead-in to `` <LOCATION> China </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Beach </LOCATION>.''
